Package: mycount
Type: Package
Title: Group Count and Incidence Rate Calculation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vicky", "S.", email = "weiyings@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    The 'mycount' package provides an easy-to-use function 'count_bio()' 
    for summarizing grouped data, extending the concept of 'dplyr::count()' 
    with additional features tailored to biostatistics and epidemiological analysis.
    It allows users to not only count observations or weighted events, 
    but also compute incidence rates (events per person-time) 
    and exact Poisson (Garwood) confidence intervals â€” commonly used 
    in cohort and clinical trial studies.
